{"tid":2429994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"再有一人接種科興後須送院　至今 4 萬人接種","createTime":"2021-03-02T15:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T15:51:04.000Z","uid":180173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a36ac0d769485b7b998b65543f0abba809f62f51","tid":2429994,"uid":180173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:46:17.000Z","msg":"繼昨日有 4 人在接種科興疫苗後要送院，今日再有一名 84 歲男子打針後感頭痛及血壓高，一度要送院檢查，但無須留院。<br />\n<br />\n政府晚上公佈，一名 84 歲男子今日到九龍灣體育館社區疫苗接種中心接種疫苗後，感到頭痛及發現血壓高，後被送往聯合醫院。他經治療及觀察後，情況穩定，無須留院。政府又指，今日有超過 13,000 名市民接種第一劑疫苗，至今累計 40,000 人已接種第一劑疫苗，超過 254,000 人已預約。<br />\n<br />\n另外，香港出現首位接種科興疫苗後死亡的個案，衞生署發稿交代，一名 63 歲男子接種疫苗後兩日不治，暫時未能確定與接種疫苗有關。<br />\n<br />\n立場: <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E5%BE%8C%E9%A0%88%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A-4-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE/?fbclid=IwAR3Gjzo6b43afoSIll63mtP0bDXJrxa_K0s1MYeP7EL-eJr02WSJJgodMSU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2588%2588%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25A0%2588%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25BB%258A-4-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Gjzo6b43afoSIll63mtP0bDXJrxa_K0s1MYeP7EL-eJr02WSJJgodMSU&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=9f3b8d3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2588%2588%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25A0%2588%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25BB%258A-4-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Gjzo6b43afoSIll63mtP0bDXJrxa_K0s1MYeP7EL-eJr02WSJJgodMSU&h=db737f9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%